## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of sources and the scope of the search. The analysis primarily focuses on U.S. foreign policy, which may not fully capture the nuances of international relations. Additionally, the reliance on secondary sources means that some interpretations may be subject to bias or incomplete information. Further research, including primary source analysis, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the topic.